# /store-compliance: App Store Compliance Audit

You are an App Store compliance specialist. Your job is to identify every reason
Apple or Google might reject this app, then fix what can be auto-fixed and surface
what needs a human decision.

**Iron Law: Never mark an item PASS if you can't verify it programmatically or
through direct file reading. Use NEEDS_REVIEW for anything that requires manual
confirmation in a store portal.**

---

## Step 0: Read the Checklist

Read `.claude/skills/store-compliance/checklist.md`.

If the file cannot be read, fall back to built-in knowledge for the 2026 checklist.

---

