## Step 3: Android / Google Play Scan (skip if `MOBILE_HAS_ANDROID=false`)

### 3.1 ŌĆö Target API Level (BLOCKER)

```bash
# Find build.gradle files with targetSdkVersion
grep -rn "targetSdkVersion\|targetSdk" \
  android/app/build.gradle android/app/build.gradle.kts \
  build.gradle build.gradle.kts 2>/dev/null | head -5
```

If `targetSdkVersion < 35` ŌåÆ BLOCKER.
AUTO-FIX: Update to `targetSdkVersion = 35` and `compileSdkVersion = 35`.

### 3.2 ŌĆö App Bundle Format (BLOCKER)

```bash
# Check that build produces .aab not .apk for store
grep -rn "assembleRelease\|bundleRelease" \
  android/app/build.gradle* Makefile Fastfile .github/workflows/ 2>/dev/null | head -5
```

If CI uses `assembleRelease` (produces `.apk`) instead of `bundleRelease` (produces `.aab`) ŌåÆ BLOCKER.
AUTO-FIX: Update CI workflow to use `./gradlew bundleRelease`.

### 3.3 ŌĆö 64-bit Support (BLOCKER)

```bash
# Check for 32-bit only native libraries
find android -name "*.so" -path "*/armeabi-v7a/*" 2>/dev/null | head -5
find android -name "*.so" -path "*/x86/*" 2>/dev/null | head -5
# Check ABI splits config
grep -rn "abiFilters\|splits.*abi" android/app/build.gradle* 2>/dev/null | head -5
```

If `armeabi-v7a` or `x86` only libraries found with no 64-bit equivalent ŌåÆ BLOCKER.

### 3.4 ŌĆö Data Safety Permissions (HIGH)

```bash
# Read AndroidManifest.xml for dangerous permissions
grep -n "uses-permission" android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml 2>/dev/null | head -30
```

List all declared permissions. For each DANGEROUS permission (CAMERA, RECORD_AUDIO,
ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION, READ_CONTACTS, etc.), flag as NEEDS_REVIEW ŌĆö must be declared
in Play Console Data Safety form.

### 3.5 ŌĆö Accessibility: contentDescription (HIGH)

```bash
# Check layout XML files for ImageView/ImageButton without contentDescription
grep -rn "<ImageView\|<ImageButton\|<FloatingActionButton" \
  android/app/src/main/res/layout/ 2>/dev/null | \
  grep -v "contentDescription" | head -10

# Check text sizes in sp vs dp/px
grep -rn 'textSize="[0-9]*dp\|textSize="[0-9]*px' \
  android/app/src/main/res/ 2>/dev/null | head -10
```

Missing `contentDescription` on image elements ŌåÆ HIGH.
Hardcoded text sizes in `dp` or `px` ŌåÆ MEDIUM (should be `sp`).
AUTO-FIX for `sp` unit conversion where safe to do so.

### 3.6 ŌĆö AI Data Disclosure (HIGH)

Same AI SDK detection as iOS Step 2.3. If found, flag for Data Safety form update
and in-app disclosure.

