## Step 4: Cross-Platform Extras

**Flutter:**
```bash
# Check for deprecated flutter_driver (should use integration_test)
grep -rn "flutter_driver" pubspec.yaml pubspec.lock 2>/dev/null | head -5

# Check for outdated dependencies
flutter pub outdated 2>/dev/null | head -20
```

**React Native / Expo:**
```bash
# Run expo doctor
npx expo-doctor 2>/dev/null | head -30

# Check SDK version
grep '"sdkVersion"\|"expo":' app.json app.config.js 2>/dev/null | head -5
```

**Both:**
```bash
# Check for Privacy Policy URL
grep -rn "privacyPolicyURL\|privacy_policy\|privacyPolicy" \
  ios/*/Info.plist android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml \
  app.json app.config.js 2>/dev/null | head -5
```

